<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗做了一个可怕的面具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都会怕我的！” 他高兴地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，他想吓一吓哈利和艾米。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，没成功。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“面具不错，奥利弗。” 哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“颜色很漂亮！” 艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，奥利弗想吓一吓爸爸、妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，奥利弗！” 爸爸给了他一个拥抱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该吃饭了，奥利弗。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚饭后，奥利弗又戴上了面具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把罗孚带到外面玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗想吓罗孚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，罗孚只是舔了舔面具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个面具一点儿也不吓人。” 奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗把面具扔到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，天就要黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该进去了。” 奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走到了前门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门被锁上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗走到了后门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门被锁上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从窗户往里看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都在看电视。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开门！” 奥利弗大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，电视声音很大，没人能听见他说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗挥舞着双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他在黑暗中，没人能看见他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗把鼻子贴在窗户上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用力敲窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 大家都尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！是奥利弗！” 艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你吓到我们了！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗咧嘴一笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可我连面具都没戴啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
